Summary: a outline of square or triangle
divs: Sighting DetailsI was on the roof watching the stars through binoculars,I saw tree line move as though a strong wind blew....no wind at the time.I was amazed at the movement of the trees,very loud like someone climbing or shaking trees I saw nothing until a few moments later,an outline of square or maybe triangle above me.....a glimmer of its edges I saw.Then it was gone,the next morning I woke up with a tiangle mark on my knee,it has been there since September of 09.I dont know what it was,I only saw outline of it from my point of view.....like dots and lines .-.-.-.-.- like this and since it was dark that was the best I could see.At first I was startled but was amused at the sound of the trees.
